HEADWORD: Steening
<hw>Steen"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A lining made of brick, stone, or
other hard material, as for a well.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>steaning</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
